README - Assignment #4

1. Processing sound library https://processing.org/reference/libraries/sound/index.html
To install library go to processing -> sketch -> add library -> search "sound" -> select and download Sound 1.4.0 by the Processing Foundation

2. Ensure the correct files are within the current processing directory. These include group_4_assignment4.pde, bensound-acousticbreeze.mp3, animateFlag.pde.

3. Press play with the group_4_assignment4.pde file open.
